{"tid":1773081,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"發現外國人最想睇到嘅文宣，其實係片","createTime":"2019-12-07T07:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T11:25:57.000Z","uid":342115,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ec730ffe079d4ee9570951c5ec362d25f27054","tid":1773081,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"小弟喺外國讀緊書，今日有幸喺讀緊嘅學校做到嘉賓講師，俾我同外國人宣傳而家香港做緊乜，以下純粹只係我自己睇到嘅嘢而作出嘅意見。<br />\n因為時間有限，所以我淨係專注屌狗，圖文加埋播片，講啲狗平時點打同點謀殺示威者。<br />\n個活動完咗之後，有好幾個人埋嚟同我講啲片好震撼，佢哋係未睇過呢啲嘢。當我喺臺上播白衫，太子嗰啲片，佢地係呆哂，因為平時佢地根本唔知邊度有得睇。<br />\n眼見好多香港嘅朋友或者黃fb專頁都會係咁分享英文文宣同畫哂圖咁，其實外國人睇完可以有咩反應？可能有幾個睇完啲文同圖會真係記住嘅，但其實好多人只係覺得 &ldquo;嘩係真係幾衰喎個政府&rdquo; 而根本印唔到件事喺心入面。<br />\n有幾多個真係俾時間睇哂啲長文？我認同有啲人畫畫真係好叻，我由心低裏佩服佢哋。但喺做文宣嘅人唔太夠嘅時候，不如分享多啲片俾人睇啦！<br />\n外國報紙，各種媒體嘅報道，點都會令佢哋對光復香港有少少概念，有啲人想知道更多嘅，可以買報紙，上網睇新聞，但好多新聞報導嘅片都剪到好短，睇到嘅嘢唔算多。<br />\n如果我哋分享多啲狗片，外國人唔洗用腦咀嚼咁多字，唔洗費神睇長文，唔洗諗啲術語究竟點解。<br />\n外國有外國嘅新聞，我哋要諗點樣喺度攝到位俾更多嘅人知道更多呢啲嘢。播片係最簡單直接嘅方法，俾著係你想睇加泰或者智利嘅示威，時間有限嘅情況下，梗係睇片啦。"},{"pid":"f363241738597f1978ab4b35ce332463cd207122","tid":1773081,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51d30a1ae629d114d13ccc8a6bcb3b2213984dbc","tid":1773081,"uid":212624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9830a7ea6357c161c4b736577fa195c508e9d5b4","tid":1773081,"uid":199200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"港大有exchange student 拍咗條片&laquo;Interia-慣性&raquo;，片入面諷刺港豬。同埋佢自已寫咗一個關於反送中嘅網站。唔知有冇用<br />\n<a href=\"https://raaghav.me/inertia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fraaghav.me%2Finertia&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=ccf6c1d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://raaghav.me/inertia</a>"},{"pid":"f0058d110bdc1009472b62b36b2ff1a856429c15","tid":1773081,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7f9f098a51f4d994dc692d1d8f408d3cf325f32","tid":1773081,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d41f143e66768a6917acf15786ca4edc4252db42","tid":1773081,"uid":199200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"56eea19bda8a8543d12a9facae4b3fe1e1e1fe24","tid":1773081,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1995c5aebc27b38cda551a3f5adfbeb19fedef3a","tid":1773081,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"11e595569283726d93282da99430733c69f367ee","tid":1773081,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"有心既睇完圖都自己搵片睇啦，就咁打幾個關鍵字都打把片"},{"pid":"b4bd006637423d253962ba118ed3eceb1f5c67df","tid":1773081,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e595569283726d93282da99430733c69f367ee","tid":1773081,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:20:05.000Z","msg":"有心既睇完圖都自己搵片睇啦，就咁打幾個關鍵字都打把片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"而家係要繼續喚醒外國人，而唔係旨意嗰少部分有心人為我哋做到啲咩，仲係有人對呢單嘢一知半解，因為係外國新聞，人哋唔主動搵但我哋可以分享更多嘢令佢願意停低花時間睇，吸收多啲。"},{"pid":"a52756f4149de4408d93e13ad96f49183148e769","tid":1773081,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}